#HTML Intro Basic

Instructions

Page with heading with your name, email, and mobile along with your favorite quote
Create a table with the names of your friends, gender, and age

HTML Code :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Info and Friends</title>
</head>
<body>
    
    <div class="info">
        <h1>Manjit Sarkar</h1>
        <p>Email: manjit.sarkar@example.com</p>
        <p>Mobile: +1234567890</p>
        <p class="quote">"The only limit to our realization of tomorrow is our doubts of today."</p>
    </div>

    <h2>My Friends</h2>

    <table>
        <tr>
            <th>Name</th>
            <th>Gender</th>
            <th>Age</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Mark</td>
            <td>Male</td>
            <td>40</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Bill</td>
            <td>Male</td>
            <td>69</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Elon</td>
            <td>Male</td>
            <td>53</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
            <td>Jeff</td>
            <td>Male</td>
            <td>61</td>
        </tr>
    </table>

</body>
</html>


CSS Code

body {
  font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
  background-color: #f4f6f8;
  color: #333;
  padding: 40px;
}

h1 {
  color: #2c3e50;
}

.info {
  margin-bottom: 30px;
}

.quote {
  font-style: italic;
  color: #555;
  margin: 20px 0;
}

table {
  width: 60%;
  border-collapse: collapse;
  margin-top: 20px;
}

th,
td {
  border: 1px solid #ccc;
  padding: 12px;
  text-align: center;
}

th {
  background-color: #2c3e50;
  color: white;
}

tr:nth-child(even) {
  background-color: #e9ecef;
}

tr:hover {
  background-color: #d6e0f0;
}
